### 1. GET Request to Retrieve All Pokemons (with pagination)
GET https://your-api-url/api/pokemon?pageNo=0&pageSize=10

### 2. GET Request to Retrieve Pokemon by ID
GET https://your-api-url/api/pokemon/1

### 3. POST Request to Create a New Pokemon
POST https://your-api-url/api/pokemon/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pikachu",
  "type": "Electric",
  "level": 5,
  "abilities": ["Static", "Lightning Rod"]
}

### 4. PUT Request to Update an Existing Pokemon
PUT https://your-api-url/api/pokemon/1/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pikachu",
  "type": "Electric",
  "level": 6,
  "abilities": ["Static", "Volt Tackle"]
}

### 5. DELETE Request to Delete a Pokemon
DELETE https://your-api-url/api/pokemon/1/delete
